{"kanda":6,"sarga":68,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"कुम्भकर्णंहतंदृष्टवाराघवेणमहात्मना ।राक्षसाराक्षसेन्द्रायरावणायन्यवेदयन्","trans":"Seeing Kumbhakarna slain by the glorious Raghava, the Rakshasas informed Ravana, the king of Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"महात्मना","m":"glorious"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णम्","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"हतम्","m":"slain"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्राय","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"रावणाय","m":"to Ravana"},{"d":"न्यवेदयन्","m":"informed."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"राजन् स कालसङ्काशस्संयुक्तःकालकर्मणा ।विद्राव्यवानरींसेनांभक्षयित्वा च वानरान्","trans":"\"O King! Kumbhakarna, who was equal to the God of Death, devoured and won over the Vanaras, scattered the army, has joined death as a consequence of time (fate).\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्","m":"king"},{"d":"कालसङ्काशः","m":"equal to god of death"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"वानरीम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"सेनाम्","m":"army"},{"d":"विद्राव्य","m":"having scattered"},{"d":"वानरान्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"भक्षयित्वा","m":"devouring"},{"d":"कालकर्मणा","m":"by consequence of time (fate)"},{"d":"संयुक्तः","m":"joined death."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"प्रतपित्वा मुहूर्तंतुप्रशान्तोरामतेजसा ।कायेनार्थप्रविष्टेनसमुद्रंभीमदर्शनम् निकृत्तकण्ठोरुभुजोविक्षरन्रुधिरंबहु ।रुद्ध्वाद्वारंशरीरेणलङ्कायाःपर्वतोपमः कुम्भकर्णस्तवभ्राताकाकुत्स्थशरपीडितः ।लगण्डभूतोविकृतोदावदग्धइवद्रुमः","trans":"\"Your brother Kumbhakarna showed his might for a short time. But by virtue of Rama's energy and arrows, his mountainlike body was reduced to a trunk of dreadful appearance. Bleeding excessively, he was like a mass submerged in an ocean of blood. like a tree caught in forest fire he was blocking the gate of Lanka in ugly form with a head, nose and ears chopped off.\"","words":[{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"भ्राता","m":"brother"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णः","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"मुहूर्तम्","m":"for a short time"},{"d":"प्रतपित्वा","m":"showed his might"},{"d":"रामतेजसा","m":