 slain, Ravana immersed in grief became deluded and fell.","words":[{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"सङ्ख्ये","m":"hearing"},{"d":"महाबलम्","m":"of great strength"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णम्","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"विनिहतम्","m":"slain"},{"d":"तम् श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing that"},{"d":"शोकसन्तप्तः","m":"immersed in grief"},{"d":"मुमोह च पपात च","m":"became deluded and fell down."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"पितृव्यंनिहतंश्रुत्वादेवान्तकनरान्तकौ ।त्रिशिराश्चातिकायश्चरुरुदुश्शोकपीडिताः","trans":"Hearing about uncle's destruction, the sons of Ravana, Devanthaka, Naranthaka, Trisira and Atikaya, roared aloud afflicted by grief.","words":[{"d":"पितृव्यम्","m":"uncle"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"देवान्तकनरान्तकौ","m":"Devantaka and Naranthaka, sons of Ravana"},{"d":"त्रिशिराः","m":"Trisira"},{"d":"अतिकायश्च","m":"Atikaya"},{"d":"शोकपीडिताः","m":"afflicted by grief"},{"d":"रुरुदुः","m":"roared aloud."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"भ्रातरंनिहतंश्रुत्वारामेणाक्लिष्टकर्मणा ।महोदरमहापार्श्वौशोकाक्रान्तौबभूवतुः","trans":"Ravana's brothers, Mahodara and Mahaparsva were overtaken by sorrow on hearing about the unwearied action of Rama and slaying of Kumbhakarna.","words":[{"d":"अक्लिष्टकर्मणा","m":"of unwearied action"},{"d":"रामेण","m":"of Rama"},{"d":"भ्रातरम्","m":"brothers"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"slain"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"महोदरमहापार्श्वौ","m":"Mahodara, Mahaparsva"},{"d":"शोकाक्रान्तौ","m":"overtaken by sorrow"},{"d":"बभूवतुः","m":"remained."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"ततःकृच्छ्रात्समासाद्यसंज्ञांराक्षसपुङ्गवः ।कुम्भकर्णवधाद्दीनोविललापकुलेन्द्रियः","trans":"Thereafter the foremost of the Rakshasas regained consciousness with great difficulty and awakened to the situation of Kumbhakarna's destruction, wailed disturbed in mind.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"राक्षसपुङ्गवः","m":"foremost of Rakshasas"},{"d":"कृच्छ्रात्","m":"with great difficulty"},{"d":"संज्ञाम्","m":"regaining"},{"d":"समासाद्य","m":"awakening"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णवधात्","m":"Kumbhakarna's killing"},{"d":"दीनः","m":"desperate"},{"d":"आकुलेन्द्रियः","m":"disturbed in mind"},{"d":"विललाप","m":"wailed."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"हावीर रिपुदर्पघ्न कुम्भकर्ण महाबल ।त्वंमांविहायवैदैवाद्यातोऽसियमसादनम्","trans":"\"Ha! Hero! Kumbhakarna! You, who crushed the pride of the enemy, endowed with great prowess have deserted me and gone to the abode of death, actually by divine will.\"","words":[{"d":"हा","m":"Ha"},{"d":"वीर","m":"hero"},{"d":"रिपुदर्पघ्न","m":"who crushed the pride of enemy"},{"d":"महाबल","m":"of great prowess"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्ण","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"माम्","m":"to me"},{"d":"विहाय","m":"deserted"},{"d":"दैवात्","m":"divine will"},{"d":"यमसादनम्","m":"abode of god of death"},{"d":"यातःअसि","m":"you actually."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"ममशल्यमनुद्धृत्यबान्धवानांमहाबल ।शत्रुसैन्यंप्रताप्यैकस्त्वंमांसन्त्यज्यगच्छसि","trans":"\"O Kumbhakarna of extraordinary might! You have tormented the enemy army singlehanded with valour. You are going alone leaving me and the kinsfolk.\"","words":[{"d":"महाबल","m":"of extraordinary might"},{"d":"मम","m":"me"},{"d":"बान्धवानाम्","m":"kin"},{"d":"शल्यम्","m":"difficulty"},{"d":"अनुद्धृत्य","m":"tormented"},{"d":"शत्रुसैन्यम्","m":"enemy army"},{"d":"प्रताप्य","m":"valour"},{"d":"एकः","m":"alone"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"सन्त्यज्य","m":"leaving"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"गच्छसि","m":"going."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"इदानींखल्वहंनास्मियस्यमेदक्षिणोभुजः ।पतितोयंसमाश्रित्य न बिभेमिसुरासुरान्","trans":"\"I who depended on you like my right arm did not fear Devatas or Danavas and I am destroyed now.\"","words":[{"d":"यस्य मे","m":"by that I"},{"d":"दक्षिणःभुजः","m":"right arm"},{"d":"पतितः","m":"fallen"},{"d":"यम्","m":"God of death"},{"d":"समाश्रित्य","m":"depending on which"},{"d":"सुरासुरात्","m":"Devatas or Danavas"},{"d":"न बिभेमि","m":"not feared"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"इदानीम्","m":"from now"},{"d":"नास्मिखलु","m":"I am destroyed."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"कथमेवंविधोवीरोदेवदानवदर्पहा ।कालाग्निरुद्राप्रतिमोरणेराघवेणवैहतः","trans":"\"You, who crushed the pride of Devas and Danavas are equal to timespirit and death at dissolution and being a hero, how did you die in the hands of Raghava?\"","words":[{"d":"देवदानवदर्पहा","m":"one who crushed the pride of Devas and Danavas"},{"d":"कालाग्निरुद्राप्रतिमः","m":"equal to time spirit and death at the time of destruction"},{"d":"एवंविधः","m":"being so"},{"d":"वीरः","m":"hero"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"कथम्","m":"how"},{"d":"हतःवै","m":"did you die?"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"यस्यतेवज्रनिष्पेषो न कुर्वाद्व्यसनंसदा ।स कथंरामबाणार्तंप्रसुप्तोऽसिमहीतले","trans":"\"You are never affected by the strike of thunderbolt. How are you sleeping on the ground hit by Rama's arrows?\"","words":[{"d":"यस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"वज्रनिष्पेषः","m":"the strike of thunderbolt"},{"d":"सदा","m":"ever"},{"d":"व्यसनम्","m":"not affect"},{"d":"न कुर्यात्","m":"not do any"},{"d":"सः","m":"that"},{"d":"रामबाणार्तः","m":"Rama's arrows"},{"d":"महीतले","m":"on ground"},{"d":"कथम्","m":"how"},{"d":"प्रसुप्तःअसि","m":"sleeping."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"एतेदेवगणास्सार्थमृषिभिर्गगनेस्थिताः ।निहतंत्वांरणेदृष्टवानिनदन्तिप्रहर्षिताः","trans":"\"These Devatas and all sages are standing in the sky, seeing the battle and laughing aloud seeing your destruction.\"","words":[{"d":"एते","m":"these"},{"d":"देवगणाः","m":"Devatas"},{"d":"ऋषिभिःसार्थम्","m":"all sages"},{"d":"गगने","m":"in the sky"},{"d":"स्थिताः","m":"stood"},{"d":"रणे","m":"battle"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"your destruction"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"प्रहर्षिताः","m":"laughing"},{"d":"निनदन्ति","m":"aloud."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"ध्रुवमद्यैवसंहृष्टालब्धलक्षाःप्लवङ्गमाः ।आरोक्ष्यन्तीहदुर्गाणिलङ्काद्वाराणिसर्वशः","trans":"\"Having found an opportunity, all the Vanaras, highly rejoiced, on this very day, will surely climb over the gates of forts of Lanka determined.\"","words":[{"d":"लब्धलक्षाः","m":"having found opportunity"},{"d":"प्लवङ्